fields.description: Go on a kayaking excursion provided by the UH Leisure Center. Excursions are lead to different parts of Oahu and are intended for the beginner kayaker. Learn kayak and water safety skills while experiencing different scenic areas around the island. Certificate expires on 12/15/2012, so you must use it this semester. Check out the [schedule of classes](http://www.manoa.hawaii.edu/studentrec/outdoored/classes.html)
fields.title: Kayaking Excursion

fields.description: Take a beginning sailing class from UH Leisure Center. This is a great opportunity to learn a great lifetime sport. Classes are taught in 20' keelboats and include both classroom and on-the-water sessions. Instruction will include basic sailing theory and concentrate on boat handling techniques at Keehi Lagoon. Certificate expires on 12/15/2012, so you must use it this semester. Find the [schedule of classes here](http://www.manoa.hawaii.edu/studentrec/outdoored/classes.html)
fields.title: Sailing class
